<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Pentecost</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">May 15, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
God of Pentecost,
</p>

 <p>
We seek the burning <br></br>
bush in the desert <br></br>
of our existence, <br></br>
never expecting that <br></br>
the fire that drew Moses <br></br>
might fall from heaven <br></br>
into our very own lives.
</p>

 <p>
Holy Spirit, come again <br></br>
to a fragmented people, <br></br>
so that we may speak <br></br>
with one voice of the <br></br>
unending love of God.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


